26
00:02:15,270 --> 00:02:16,110
or he wouldn't have

27
00:02:16,110 --> 00:02:17,570
put this store up for sale.

28
00:02:18,610 --> 00:02:20,190
The location is great.

29
00:02:21,700 --> 00:02:22,720
But now,

30
00:02:23,220 --> 00:02:24,480
