31
00:02:24,620 --> 00:02:26,750
Can you reserve it for us for a few days?

32
00:02:27,090 --> 00:02:27,860
Of course.

33
00:02:28,950 --> 00:02:29,600
As long as

34
00:02:29,630 --> 00:02:30,780
you pay the deposit.

35
00:02:32,390 --> 00:02:32,829
Well,

36
00:02:32,850 --> 00:02:33,980
please do us a favor.

37
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,670
After we scrape together enough money,

38
00:02:35,670 --> 00:02:37,150
