39
00:02:37,390 --> 00:02:38,390
What do you think?

40
00:02:39,110 --> 00:02:41,390
You don't have money but want to buy a store?

41
00:02:41,390 --> 00:02:41,800
We…

42
00:02:41,820 --> 00:02:42,420
Five days.

43
00:02:42,990 --> 00:02:43,680
Just five days.

44
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,280
Five days?

45
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:45,680
No.

46
