53
00:02:58,390 --> 00:02:58,900
Deal.

54
00:02:59,100 --> 00:02:59,540
Okay.

55
00:02:59,980 --> 00:03:01,220
See you in three days.

56
00:03:01,930 --> 00:03:02,530
Thank you.

57
