94
00:04:30,470 --> 00:04:31,030
Otherwise,

95
00:04:31,030 --> 00:04:32,690
don't blame us for being rude.

96
00:04:37,710 --> 00:04:38,150
Okay.

97
00:04:38,610 --> 00:04:39,620
We'll go with you.

98
00:04:40,220 --> 00:04:40,750
