115
00:05:40,590 --> 00:05:41,790
Don't worry about it.

116
00:05:41,940 --> 00:05:42,570
Leave this matter

117
00:05:42,570 --> 00:05:43,530
to me.

118
00:05:44,020 --> 00:05:45,020
Let's go back now.

119
00:05:45,350 --> 00:05:46,100
Thirteen must be

120
00:05:46,100 --> 00:05:47,560
