121
00:06:04,190 --> 00:06:04,960
Chang Feng.

122
00:06:05,660 --> 00:06:08,540
I want to learn how to write your name.

123
00:06:08,830 --> 00:06:09,820
Try it.

124
00:06:11,530 --> 00:06:13,020
Something is going on between them.

125
00:06:13,020 --> 00:06:13,750
Impossible.

126
00:06:14,650 --> 00:06:16,110
I know Thirteen very well.

127
00:06:16,440 --> 00:06:17,540
They can't be together.

128
00:06:17,540 --> 00:06:19,120
They'll be together very soon.

129
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,780
It's absolutely impossible.

130
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:28,340
What's wrong with him?

131
00:07:06,850 --> 00:07:07,730
Young Master.

132
00:07:07,750 --> 00:07:08,900
