134
00:07:09,710 --> 00:07:11,170
Don't look at me like that.

135
00:07:11,470 --> 00:07:12,590
I can't stand it.

136
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,400
Thirteen, let me ask you.

137
00:07:16,020 --> 00:07:17,750
You like Lian Ye'er, don't you?

138
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:19,880
No. That's nonsense.

139
00:07:23,870 --> 00:07:24,520
Good.

140
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:27,600
You like Miss Man'er.

141
00:07:28,460 --> 00:07:29,150
Why can't I

142
00:07:29,170 --> 00:07:30,190
like Ye'er?

143
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:35,470
The location

144
00:07:36,060 --> 00:07:38,060
of the store we found today is great.

145
00:07:38,180 --> 00:07:39,380
If we can buy it,

146
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,040
business won't be bad.

147
00:07:42,150 --> 00:07:43,140
Black Tiger Fortress

148
00:07:43,140 --> 00:07:44,400
owes us a batch of wine.

149
00:07:44,670 --> 00:07:46,400
If we can get it back and sell it,

150
00:07:46,500 --> 00:07:47,340
we'll have money

151
00:07:47,340 --> 00:07:48,270
to buy the store.

152
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:50,500
For those at Black Tiger Fortress,

153
00:07:50,500 --> 00:07:51,630
money is important,

154
00:07:51,909 --> 00:07:53,170
but there's something

155
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:54,530
more important to them.

156
00:07:54,940 --> 00:07:56,270
I'll go get it tomorrow.

157
00:07:58,230 --> 00:07:58,700
Okay.

158
00:08:10,660 --> 00:08:11,460
Young Master.

159
00:08:11,890 --> 00:08:14,210
What do you think of Miss Ye'er?

160
00:08:15,190 --> 00:08:16,520
What do you think of her?

161
00:08:17,780 --> 00:08:18,590
I think

162
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:20,700
she's amazing.

163
00:08:23,590 --> 00:08:24,650
Come to think of it,

164
00:08:25,670 --> 00:08:27,470
if I and Miss Ye'er are together,

165
00:08:28,230 --> 00:08:28,890
I'll become

166
00:08:28,910 --> 00:08:30,570
your brother-in-law, right?

167
00:08:33,140 --> 00:08:33,940
Young Master.

168
00:08:35,500 --> 00:08:36,299
Young Master?

169
00:08:38,990 --> 00:08:41,120
The relationship is too complicated.

170
00:09:04,370 --> 00:09:07,360
Oh, my heavens!

171
00:09:08,310 --> 00:09:10,300
What should I do?

172
00:09:10,300 --> 00:09:11,070
He.

173
00:09:11,170 --> 00:09:11,840
What happened, Dad?

174
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:12,520
Get up.

175
00:09:12,940 --> 00:09:13,800
What happened?

176
00:09:14,290 --> 00:09:16,150
Your Aunt He gave the money

177
00:09:16,180 --> 00:09:17,440
to your Uncle Shouren.

178
00:09:18,150 --> 00:09:19,990
But Shouren took the money

179
00:09:20,390 --> 00:09:21,390
and disappeared.

180
00:09:22,460 --> 00:09:24,180
Seems that Shouyi

181
00:09:24,310 --> 00:09:25,840
can't survive it this time.

182
00:09:26,870 --> 00:09:28,030
Uncle Shouren disappeared.

183
00:09:28,030 --> 00:09:29,030
How about Aunt Gu?

184
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:31,010
She ran away too.

185
00:09:36,350 --> 00:09:37,440
He told me

186
00:09:38,110 --> 00:09:39,340
that as long as I had money,

187
00:09:39,340 --> 00:09:40,730
he could bribe the government

188
00:09:40,730 --> 00:09:42,140
to release Shouyi.

189
00:09:42,900 --> 00:09:43,740
I…

190
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:46,560
I lost my mind and shamelessly

191
00:09:46,590 --> 00:09:48,630
stole money from my own family.

192
00:09:49,820 --> 00:09:52,540
Shouren just left me in the lurch.

193
00:09:55,160 --> 00:09:56,760
I don't want to live anymore.

194
00:09:57,430 --> 00:09:58,930
Let me die!

195
00:09:59,270 --> 00:10:00,950
He! He!

196
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:02,940
What are you doing?

197
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:04,040
You can't do this.

198
00:10:04,790 --> 00:10:06,270
Don't do this.

199
00:10:06,790 --> 00:10:08,600
-Fang…
-Don't do this.

200
00:10:08,700 --> 00:10:09,230
Fang.

201
00:10:09,380 --> 00:10:10,310
-Grandpa.
-Dad.

202
00:10:10,310 --> 00:10:10,840
Grandpa!

203
00:10:10,920 --> 00:10:11,460
Are you okay?

204
00:10:11,460 --> 00:10:12,120
Don't move.

205
00:10:12,210 --> 00:10:12,930
I'm fine.

206
00:10:12,970 --> 00:10:13,700
Are you okay?

207
00:10:14,110 --> 00:10:14,830
I'm fine.

208
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:17,960
I'm just having palpitations. I'm fine.

209
00:10:21,190 --> 00:10:21,830
He.

210
00:10:23,110 --> 00:10:24,320
It's not your fault.

211
00:10:25,100 --> 00:10:26,710
It's Shouren's fault.

212
00:10:29,230 --> 00:10:29,990
San'er.

213
00:10:32,580 --> 00:10:33,530
Go to the town

214
00:10:34,270 --> 00:10:35,710
