215
00:10:36,710 --> 00:10:38,190
Bring Shouren back.

216
00:10:39,140 --> 00:10:40,750
Tell him I want him back.

217
00:10:50,710 --> 00:10:51,580
He, what are you doing?

218
00:10:51,580 --> 00:10:52,110
Shouxin.

219
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,080
I'll count on you

220
00:10:56,180 --> 00:10:57,700
to save Shouyi.

221
00:10:58,700 --> 00:10:59,470
He.

222
00:10:59,710 --> 00:11:00,950
Get up.

223
00:11:00,970 --> 00:11:01,520
Get up.

224
00:11:01,550 --> 00:11:02,930
-No!
-You…

225
00:11:04,260 --> 00:11:05,210
You…

226
00:11:05,830 --> 00:11:07,310
I'll go find Shouren now.

227
00:11:08,710 --> 00:11:09,640
I'll go with you.

228
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:10,810
Get up.

229
00:11:11,940 --> 00:11:12,580
Get up, He.

230
00:11:14,190 --> 00:11:15,340
Come on. Get up.

