232
00:11:37,010 --> 00:11:37,750
Shouren.

233
00:11:39,060 --> 00:11:39,830
Shouren.

234
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:41,940
Uncle Shouren!

235
00:11:44,590 --> 00:11:45,070
Sir.

236
00:11:45,340 --> 00:11:45,950
Do you know

237
00:11:45,980 --> 00:11:47,780
