239
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:51,130
-Moved away?
-What?

240
00:11:51,130 --> 00:11:52,130
Where did they go?

241
00:11:52,470 --> 00:11:53,470
Are you

242
00:11:53,620 --> 00:11:55,010
their relatives?

243
00:11:59,550 --> 00:12:00,560
Before they left,

244
00:12:00,590 --> 00:12:01,390
they warned me

245
00:12:01,510 --> 00:12:02,190
about relatives

246
00:12:02,190 --> 00:12:03,520
who often came to borrow money

247
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:04,700
and were hard to get rid of.

248
00:12:04,700 --> 00:12:06,430
He told me to stay away from you.

249
00:12:11,870 --> 00:12:13,100
Man'er.

250
00:12:13,870 --> 00:12:15,180
What should we do now?

251
00:12:18,230 --> 00:12:19,110
We

252
00:12:19,780 --> 00:12:21,510
have forgotten about someone.

253
00:12:26,030 --> 00:12:27,790
I don't know where my father is.

254
00:12:28,070 --> 00:12:29,330
You must know.

255
00:12:29,740 --> 00:12:31,830
Your father took the money and ran away.

256
00:12:31,830 --> 00:12:33,230
Uncle Shouyi will have to go to jail.

257
00:12:33,230 --> 00:12:33,950
Aunt He

258
00:12:34,300 --> 00:12:35,520
cried her eyes out at home.

259
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:36,970
