263
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:43,160
Why are you here arguing with me?

264
00:12:46,190 --> 00:12:46,700
Fine.

265
00:12:47,680 --> 00:12:48,810
If you don't tell me,

266
00:12:49,190 --> 00:12:50,450
I'll ask your in-laws.

267
00:12:50,700 --> 00:12:51,430
Lian Man'er!

268
00:12:53,820 --> 00:12:55,100
Don't go too far.

269
00:12:58,990 --> 00:13:00,790
You're still in the Song Mansion

270
00:13:02,040 --> 00:13:03,500
yet your parents ran away.

271
00:13:04,190 --> 00:13:05,340
