275
00:13:18,430 --> 00:13:19,060
Hua'er.

276
00:13:20,590 --> 00:13:22,250
I know life is hard for you too.

277
00:13:22,420 --> 00:13:23,830
If things weren't messed up at home,

278
00:13:23,830 --> 00:13:25,360
I wouldn't have come to you.

279
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:26,640
You just need to tell me

280
00:13:26,640 --> 00:13:27,970
where your parents are.

281
00:13:28,350 --> 00:13:29,870
Once you tell me, I'll leave.

282
00:13:29,870 --> 00:13:30,840
The Song family won't know

283
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:31,700
I've been here.

284
00:13:34,350 --> 00:13:35,310
Why do you think

285
00:13:35,750 --> 00:13:36,810
life is hard for me?

286
00:13:42,030 --> 00:13:43,590
I've been required to learn the etiquette

287
00:13:43,590 --> 00:13:45,450
in high society since I was young.

288
00:13:46,570 --> 00:13:47,440
Do you really think my father

289
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:48,440
dotes on me?

290
00:13:49,810 --> 00:13:51,750
After I finally married into the Song family,

291
00:13:51,750 --> 00:13:52,990
I begged and begged

292
00:13:53,860 --> 00:13:56,460
but still couldn't get anything for my father.

293
00:13:57,100 --> 00:13:57,860
