resigned due to illness.

593
00:27:52,350 --> 00:27:53,530
I'm expected

594
00:27:53,710 --> 00:27:55,100
to start working as soon as possible.

595
00:27:55,100 --> 00:27:55,750
So,

596
00:27:56,030 --> 00:27:56,970
without further delay,

597
00:27:56,970 --> 00:27:58,230
I'll set off tomorrow.

598
00:27:58,370 --> 00:27:59,250
So soon?

599
00:28:02,790 --> 00:28:03,190
I see.

600
00:28:03,550 --> 00:28:04,970
Then we have to hurry up.

601
00:28:05,440 --> 00:28:07,040
We mustn't hold you up.

602
00:28:07,310 --> 00:28:08,120
He.

603
00:28:08,900 --> 00:28:09,540
Well,

604
00:28:09,990 --> 00:28:11,030
go back and pack up.

605
00:28:11,030 --> 00:28:11,490
Pack up.

606
00:28:11,520 --> 00:28:13,100
-Throw away unnecessary things.
-Okay.

607
00:28:13,100 --> 00:28:14,060
Don't pack too much.

608
00:28:14,060 --> 00:28:14,930
I know.

609
00:28:16,100 --> 00:28:16,670
Shouyi.

610
00:28:17,240 --> 00:28:18,200
I'm about to start working.

611
00:28:18,200 --> 00:28:19,750
Why do you need to throw things away?

612
00:28:19,750 --> 00:28:21,410
So that you can buy us new ones.

613
00:28:24,240 --> 00:28:26,400
You're going with me?

614
00:28:26,670 --> 00:28:28,000
-Of course.
-Of course.

615
00:28:28,320 --> 00:28:29,920
We talked about this before.

616
00:28:30,370 --> 00:28:31,670
After you become an official,

617
00:28:31,670 --> 00:28:32,910
you'll help us live a better life.

618
00:28:32,910 --> 00:28:33,830
Now that you did,

619
00:28:33,830 --> 00:28:34,530
we'll stick with you.

620
00:28:34,530 --> 00:28:35,300
Yeah.

621
00:28:35,430 --> 00:28:35,860
No.

622
00:28:36,070 --> 00:28:36,630
Shouren.

623
00:28:36,990 --> 00:28:38,260
We're family.

624
00:28:38,370 --> 00:28:40,170
Families stick together.

625
00:28:40,270 --> 00:28:41,840
How can we let you

626
00:28:42,030 --> 00:28:43,390
start working all alone?

627
00:28:43,390 --> 00:28:45,430
Dad and Mom would be worried.

628
00:28:45,520 --> 00:28:48,020
Yeah. I'm about to start working

629
00:28:48,390 --> 00:28:50,470
and don't want to leave Dad and Mom.

630
00:28:50,850 --> 00:28:51,440
But

631
00:28:51,790 --> 00:28:53,670
have you ever heard of any bookkeeping official

632
00:28:53,670 --> 00:28:55,410
who brought his whole family to work?

633
00:28:55,410 --> 00:28:57,560
I'm just a bookkeeping official

634
00:28:57,590 --> 00:28:58,920
who is even below Rank 9.

635
00:28:58,930 --> 00:29:00,070
-Above me…
-So what?

636
00:29:00,880 --> 00:29:02,680
Officials don't have families?

637
00:29:03,030 --> 00:29:03,970
Officials

638
00:29:04,200 --> 00:29:05,580
don't have parents

639
00:29:05,610 --> 00:29:06,560
and brothers?

640
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:08,680
Fine.

641
00:29:08,730 --> 00:29:10,450
He, don't get me wrong.

642
00:29:10,470 --> 00:29:11,720
Shouren, take no offense.

643
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:12,870
You know your sister-in-law.

644
00:29:12,870 --> 00:29:14,760
She doesn't think before she talks.

645
00:29:14,760 --> 00:29:15,630
We're brothers.

646
00:29:15,630 --> 00:29:16,820
I know you.

647
00:29:17,230 --> 00:29:18,630
Abandoning your parents

648
00:29:18,730 --> 00:29:20,950
and siblings after becoming an official

649
00:29:20,950 --> 00:29:23,120
is not something you would do.

650
00:29:29,180 --> 00:29:30,890
Are you still angry

651
00:29:30,930 --> 00:29:32,660
about what happened yesterday?

652
00:29:32,660 --> 00:29:33,940
No.

653
00:29:35,330 --> 00:29:37,010
I just got out of prison

654
00:29:37,830 --> 00:29:39,560
and wasn't thinking straight.

655
00:29:39,700 --> 00:29:40,730
Please forgive me.

656
00:29:40,730 --> 00:29:42,210
Shouyi, you…

657
00:29:42,600 --> 00:29:44,230
If you're still angry with me,

658
00:29:44,230 --> 00:29:45,140
you can hit me.

659
00:29:45,540 --> 00:29:46,340
I'm not angry.

660
00:29:47,230 --> 00:29:47,830
Okay.

661
00:29:48,310 --> 00:29:49,430
We're good now.

662
00:29:49,700 --> 00:29:51,050
Let's drink.

663
00:29:52,810 --> 00:29:53,520
Dad.

664
00:30:19,770 --> 00:30:20,210
Mom.

665
00:30:20,710 --> 00:30:22,140
This village

666
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:23,320
is a good place.

667
00:30:24,130 --> 00:30:25,910
It's much better than the city.

668
00:30:26,210 --> 00:30:28,020
All the major criminals in nearby towns

669
00:30:28,020 --> 00:30:29,410
are kept in the city.

670
00:30:29,990 --> 00:30:32,110
I know what you want to say.

671
00:30:32,740 --> 00:30:35,200
You're worried that I'll go to live with you.

672
00:30:35,230 --> 00:30:35,940
Think about it.

673
00:30:35,940 --> 00:30:37,870
You and your wife have been living in town.

674
00:30:37,870 --> 00:30:39,350
It's not far from here.

675
00:30:39,660 --> 00:30:41,320
Have I ever gone to your house?

676
00:30:41,500 --> 00:30:42,030
Mom.

677
00:30:42,170 --> 00:30:43,610
You misunderstand me.

678
00:30:43,990 --> 00:30:44,840
There's no place

679
00:30:44,840 --> 00:30:46,140
like home.

680
00:30:46,450 --> 00:30:47,510
If you leave behind

681
00:30:47,760 --> 00:30:48,230
those

682
00:30:48,620 --> 00:30:50,280
chickens, ducks, pigs, cows,

683
00:30:50,590 --> 00:30:51,390
and the field,

684
00:30:51,470 --> 00:30:52,710
who will take care of them?

685
00:30:52,710 --> 00:30:53,180
Right.

686
00:30:53,210 --> 00:30:53,800
Besides,

687
00:30:53,920 --> 00:30:56,470
you worked hard for years

688
00:30:57,190 --> 00:30:58,550
to get everything you have now.

689
00:30:58,550 --> 00:30:59,680
If you're gone for long,

690
00:30:59,680 --> 00:31:01,810
who knows if anyone's gonna take them?

691
00:31:03,570 --> 00:31:04,880
You have a point.

692
00:31:05,580 --> 00:31:06,220
But

693
00:31:07,180 --> 00:31:08,980
I need to ask your dad's opinion.

694
00:31:09,490 --> 00:31:10,570
No one knows my dad

695
00:31:10,600 --> 00:31:12,080
better than me.

696
00:31:12,700 --> 00:31:13,670
He only has two wishes.

697
00:31:13,670 --> 00:31:15,000
One is that I could become an official.

698
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:16,000
It has come true.

699
00:31:16,270 --> 00:31:16,700
Right?

700
00:31:16,980 --> 00:31:17,720
The other

701
00:31:17,990 --> 00:31:19,850
is that Xiu'er could get married.

702
00:31:20,340 --> 00:31:21,980
If you two leave,

703
00:31:22,310 --> 00:31:24,640
it'll be harder for Xiu'er to get married.

704
00:31:25,830 --> 00:31:27,260
Why?

705
00:31:27,890 --> 00:31:28,750
Think about it.

706
00:31:29,000 --> 00:31:29,750
Family image

707
00:31:30,290 --> 00:31:31,730
matters a lot in marriage.

708
00:31:31,730 --> 00:31:33,270
If you all moved into the city

709
00:31:33,270 --> 00:31:34,370
with me,

710
00:31:34,790 --> 00:31:36,210
we'd be seen as displaced,

711
00:31:36,210 --> 00:31:37,550
disgraceful,

712
00:31:37,590 --> 00:31:38,390
and pathetic.

713
00:31:38,460 --> 00:31:40,590
No one would want to marry Xiu'er then.

714
00:31:41,350 --> 00:31:43,550
But things are difficult in the village.

715
00:31:43,550 --> 00:31:44,680
Now that I, your son,

716
00:31:44,830 --> 00:31:46,350
have become an official,

717
00:31:46,610 --> 00:31:48,400
I'm no longer a nobody.

718
00:31:48,870 --> 00:31:49,390
You

719
00:31:49,550 --> 00:31:51,430
are the mother of an official.

720
00:31:51,780 --> 00:31:52,420
Xiu'er

721
00:31:52,480 --> 00:31:54,080
is the sister of an official.

722
00:31:54,240 --> 00:31:54,970
Don't worry.

723
00:31:55,340 --> 00:31:56,540
I'll find a good match

724
00:31:57,420 --> 00:31:58,350
for Xiu'er.

725
00:32:00,260 --> 00:32:00,860
Shouren.

726
00:32:01,730 --> 00:32:03,300
Do you mean what you said?

727
00:32:04,070 --> 00:32:05,460
Then I'll count you

728
00:32:06,230 --> 00:32:07,780
to marry Xiu'er off.

729
00:32:08,650 --> 00:32:09,860
You can't leave home

730
00:32:09,890 --> 00:32:11,280
for a better life

731
00:32:11,550 --> 00:32:12,910
and forget all

732
00:32:13,220 --> 00:32:14,370
about us.

733
00:32:14,440 --> 00:32:15,780
Don't worry.

734
00:32:16,130 --> 00:32:17,410
It's settled then.

735
00:32:18,250 --> 00:32:19,170
Let me help you.

736
00:32:19,200 --> 00:32:19,670
No need.

737
00:32:19,740 --> 00:32:21,660
I can do it.

738
00:32:21,680 --> 00:32:22,570
No need.

739
00:32:22,760 --> 00:32:24,360
Mom.

740
00:32:24,560 --> 00:32:27,000
Can you talk to Shouyi and his wife for me?

741
00:32:27,380 --> 00:32:28,450
Tell them

742
00:32:28,480 --> 00:32:29,560
to get off my back.

743
00:32:30,760 --> 00:32:32,510
Your dad and I are not going.

744
00:32:32,880 --> 00:32:34,030
Shouyi and his wife

745
00:32:34,590 --> 00:32:36,010
will surely stay here too.

746
00:32:36,010 --> 00:32:36,470
Okay.

747
00:32:36,490 --> 00:32:37,690
-Don't worry.
-Okay.

748
00:32:37,830 --> 00:32:39,920
Mom, let me help you.

749
00:32:45,390 --> 00:32:45,950
How's it?

750
00:32:47,400 --> 00:32:48,240
We can't

751
00:32:48,270 --> 00:32:49,330
move into the city.

752
00:32:49,620 --> 00:32:50,230
Why?

753
00:32:50,680 --> 00:32:51,740
Shouren brought up

754
00:32:51,760 --> 00:32:52,890
Xiu'er's marriage.

755
00:32:53,020 --> 00:32:54,540
He promised to find a good match for her.

756
00:32:54,540 --> 00:32:55,210
Mom changed her mind

757
00:32:55,210 --> 00:32:56,340
and decided to stay.

758
00:32:56,630 --> 00:32:57,510
Darn it.

759
00:32:58,080 --> 00:32:58,870
I knew it.

760
00:32:59,350 --> 00:33:00,660
Shouren is an ingrate.

761
00:33:01,180 --> 00:33:03,060
He's going to work in the city without us.

762
00:33:03,060 --> 00:33:04,190
He wants to dump us

763
00:33:04,260 --> 00:33:05,420
and enjoy his life.

764
00:33:08,420 --> 00:33:08,900
No.

765
00:33:09,610 --> 00:33:12,470
We must extort some money from him before he leaves.

766
00:33:13,450 --> 00:33:14,310
Think about it.

767
00:33:14,860 --> 00:33:15,790
When you were in jail,

768
00:33:15,790 --> 00:33:16,600
what did he do?

769
00:33:17,230 --> 00:33:19,110
He fooled me into stealing Man'er's money.

770
00:33:19,110 --> 00:33:21,440
He deserves worse than being shaken down.

771
00:33:22,350 --> 00:33:22,980
Remember.

772
00:33:23,590 --> 00:33:24,550
He owes us.

773
00:33:25,340 --> 00:33:26,600
We must shake him down.

774
00:33:27,060 --> 00:33:27,770
How?

775
00:33:49,010 --> 00:33:50,370
Brother, it's me.

776
00:33:50,880 --> 00:33:51,490
Shouyi?

777
00:33:54,430 --> 00:33:55,470
What's wrong

778
00:33:55,860 --> 00:33:57,230
with you two?

779
00:33:57,520 --> 00:33:58,610
What are you doing?

780
00:33:59,680 --> 00:34:00,210
Shouren.

781
00:34:00,570 --> 00:34:01,450
Look at you.

782
00:34:02,130 --> 00:34:04,340
Are you running away in the middle of the night?

783
00:34:04,340 --> 00:34:04,940
Nonsense.

784
00:34:05,770 --> 00:34:06,970
Get your hands off me.

785
00:34:07,060 --> 00:34:07,980
You're so rude.

786
00:34:10,670 --> 00:34:11,230
Shouren.

787
00:34:11,620 --> 00:34:13,090
You haven't started working yet

788
00:34:13,090 --> 00:34:15,219
but are already giving yourself airs.

789
00:34:15,460 --> 00:34:16,900
Let me guess.

790
00:34:17,280 --> 00:34:19,440
You must've brought up

791
00:34:19,710 --> 00:34:21,040
Xiu'er's marriage again

792
00:34:21,040 --> 00:34:22,239
to change Mom's mind.

793
00:34:25,670 --> 00:34:26,989
You two twerps!

794
00:34:27,940 --> 00:34:28,909
Can't you give up

795
00:34:28,929 --> 00:34:30,260
the habit of eavesdropping?

796
00:34:30,260 --> 00:34:30,790
No.

797
00:34:33,580 --> 00:34:34,219
I see.

798
00:34:34,630 --> 00:34:36,630
It's about me going to work in the city,

799
00:34:36,630 --> 00:34:37,159
isn't it?

800
00:34:37,179 --> 00:34:38,909
That's why you stopped me here.

801
00:34:39,460 --> 00:34:42,070
I never said you couldn't go with me.

802
00:34:42,400 --> 00:34:45,190
I've made a thorough plan.

803
00:34:46,449 --> 00:34:47,639
I'll go first

804
00:34:48,030 --> 00:34:50,469
and arrange everything for you.

805
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:53,120
Then you'll come.

806
00:34:53,670 --> 00:34:54,550
This is the best

807
00:34:54,960 --> 00:34:56,330
for all of us, isn't it?

808
00:34:56,590 --> 00:34:57,600
When you arrive,

809
00:34:57,690 --> 00:34:59,350
everything will be prepared.

810
00:34:59,860 --> 00:35:00,860
Isn't that great?

811
00:35:02,170 --> 00:35:03,220
You're so considerate.

812
00:35:03,220 --> 00:35:04,020
Rest assured.

813
00:35:05,230 --> 00:35:06,230
I'm not finished.

814
00:35:06,860 --> 00:35:07,700
Say no more.

815
00:35:07,900 --> 00:35:09,830
Shouren is not that kind of person.

816
00:35:09,830 --> 00:35:10,760
Right, Shouren?

817
00:35:10,910 --> 00:35:11,340
Yeah.

818
00:35:11,840 --> 00:35:13,370
Shouren, here's the thing.

819
00:35:13,690 --> 00:35:15,420
You're about to start working.

820
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:17,770
Just a teeny-tiny bit of money

821
00:35:18,110 --> 00:35:19,510
out of your deep pockets,

822
00:35:20,070 --> 00:35:21,030
just a tiny bit of it,

823
00:35:21,030 --> 00:35:22,760
is enough to last us for a while.

824
00:35:23,080 --> 00:35:23,710
Vulgar!

825
00:35:24,590 --> 00:35:25,430
Can't you two

826
00:35:25,560 --> 00:35:26,340
think about something

827
00:35:26,340 --> 00:35:27,340
other than money?

828
00:35:27,590 --> 00:35:28,740
In that case…

829
00:35:29,740 --> 00:35:31,200
Shouren, don't go. You...

830
00:35:31,260 --> 00:35:31,860
Shouyi.

831
00:35:32,050 --> 00:35:33,180
You can't take that.

832
00:35:33,450 --> 00:35:34,370
Help!

833
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:35,650
There's a murder here!

834
00:35:35,650 --> 00:35:38,010
This man is trying to kill his brother!

835
00:35:38,060 --> 00:35:38,460
You…

836
00:35:38,880 --> 00:35:41,610
This murderer is going to work in the government!

837
00:35:44,070 --> 00:35:44,740
Don't shout.

838
00:35:44,740 --> 00:35:45,810
Don't shout.

839
00:35:46,300 --> 00:35:47,310
How much do you want?

840
00:35:47,310 --> 00:35:47,920
Tell me.

841
00:35:50,040 --> 00:35:51,170
That's more like it.

842
00:35:56,650 --> 00:36:04,250
[Song]

843
00:36:06,220 --> 00:36:06,910
Hua'er.

844
00:36:18,870 --> 00:36:19,990
Sorry, Hua'er.

845
00:36:20,870 --> 00:36:22,930
We shouldn't have hidden behind you.

846
00:36:23,930 --> 00:36:25,660
Did Man'er give you a hard time?

847
00:36:29,270 --> 00:36:30,750
Thanks to you,

848
00:36:31,210 --> 00:36:33,880
your father has become the bookkeeping official.

849
00:36:33,880 --> 00:36:34,480
Well,

850
00:36:34,820 --> 00:36:36,480
the moment we waited for years

851
00:36:36,630 --> 00:36:38,140
finally came.

852
00:36:39,750 --> 00:36:41,230
You should look for an opportunity

853
00:36:41,230 --> 00:36:42,740
to beg Hailong again.

854
00:36:43,540 --> 00:36:44,320
Maybe

855
00:36:44,860 --> 00:36:46,520
your father can get promoted.

856
00:36:52,200 --> 00:36:52,750
Mom.

857
00:36:55,750 --> 00:36:56,540
It was hard for me

858
00:36:56,540 --> 00:36:58,270
to convince Hailong to help me.

859
00:36:58,680 --> 00:36:59,950
He spent lots of money and effort

860
00:36:59,950 --> 00:37:01,190
in making connections

861
00:37:01,190 --> 00:37:02,280
so that Dad could finally

862
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:03,360
get this position.

863
00:37:04,200 --> 00:37:05,140
Dad hasn't even

864
00:37:05,160 --> 00:37:05,850
started working

865
00:37:05,850 --> 00:37:08,050
yet you're thinking about promotions.

866
00:37:09,860 --> 00:37:11,350
I was just saying.

867
00:37:12,060 --> 00:37:14,060
Calm down. Don't take it seriously.

868
00:37:14,350 --> 00:37:15,090
Hua'er.

869
00:37:22,550 --> 00:37:23,070
Hua'er.

870
00:37:23,980 --> 00:37:25,840
You married into the Song family.

871
00:37:26,860 --> 00:37:27,950
You married up

872
00:37:27,970 --> 00:37:28,970
and are living

873
00:37:28,990 --> 00:37:30,190
an enviable life now.

874
00:37:30,770 --> 00:37:32,750
I'm truly happy for you.

875
00:37:34,220 --> 00:37:34,820
How about…

876
00:37:35,090 --> 00:37:35,780
How about

877
00:37:35,850 --> 00:37:37,620
we have dinner together tomorrow?

878
00:37:37,620 --> 00:37:38,950
Bring Hailong with you.

879
00:37:39,190 --> 00:37:40,360
Your father

880
00:37:40,500 --> 00:37:41,700
can have a drink with him.

881
00:37:41,700 --> 00:37:42,370
No need.

882
00:37:52,030 --> 00:37:52,830
I understand.

883
00:37:55,100 --> 00:37:56,430
Hailong must be too busy

884
00:37:57,070 --> 00:37:57,930
to dine with us.

885
00:38:00,500 --> 00:38:01,670
Have you heard

886
00:38:01,700 --> 00:38:02,900
about Man'er's plan?

